{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"File.getAsDataURL()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File/getAsDataURL","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File_API\">File API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File/File\"><code>File()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File/lastModified\"><code>lastModified</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File/lastModifiedDate\"><code>lastModifiedDate</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File/name\"><code>name</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File/type\"><code>type</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File/webkitRelativePath\"><code>webkitRelativePath</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for File API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileList\"><code>FileList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileReader\"><code>FileReader</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileReaderSync\"><code>FileReaderSync</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URL/createObjectURL\"><code>URL.createObjectURL()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URL/revokeObjectURL\"><code>URL.revokeObjectURL()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard warning\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>非标准:</strong> 该特性是非标准的，请尽量不要在生产环境中使用它！</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard deprecated\" id=\"sect3\"><p><strong>已废弃 Gecko 7.0 (Firefox 7.0 / Thunderbird 7.0 / SeaMonkey 2.4):</strong> 该特性已经从 Web 标准中删除，虽然一些浏览器目前仍然支持它，但也许会在未来的某个时间停止支持，请尽量不要使用该特性。</p></div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"概述","title":"概述","isH3":false,"content":"<p>getAsDataURL<code>函数返回一个形如 </code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Basics_of_HTTP/Data_URLs\"><code>data:</code></a> 的 URL，这个 URL 包含了所涉及到的内容的编码形式。</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect4\">\n<p><strong>注：</strong> 这个方法已经废弃，你应该使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileReader\"><code>FileReader</code></a> 对象中的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsDataURL\" title=\"readAsDataURL()\"><code>readAsDataURL()</code></a> 方法作为替代。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">var url = <em>instanceOfFile</em>.getAsDataURL();</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<p>一个形如 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Basics_of_HTTP/Data_URLs\"><code>data:</code></a> 的 URL 字符串</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"范例","title":"范例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// fileInput 是一个 HTMLInputElement 元素：&lt;input type=\"file\" id=\"myfileinput\" multiple&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> fileInput <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"myfileinput\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// files 是一个 FileList 对象 (类似 NodeList 对象)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> files <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> fileInput<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>files<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 允许的文件格式数组</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> accept <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"image/png\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// img 是一个 HTMLImgElement 元素：&lt;img id=\"myimg\"&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> img <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"myimg\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 假设我们接收第一个所选中的文件类型</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>accept<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">indexOf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>files<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mediaType<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// 显示图片</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// 和 &lt;img src=\"data:image/png,&lt;imagedata&gt;\"&gt; 效果一样</span>\n  img<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>src <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> files<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getAsDataURL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"详细说明","title":"详细说明","isH3":false,"content":"<p>没有其他说明</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参考文章","title":"参考文章","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileReader\"><code>FileReader</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"概述","id":"概述"},{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"范例","id":"范例"},{"text":"详细说明","id":"详细说明"},{"text":"参考文章","id":"参考文章"}],"summary":"getAsDataURL函数返回一个形如 data: 的 URL，这个 URL 包含了所涉及到的内容的编码形式。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"File.getAsDataURL()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/file/getasdataurl","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/file/getasdataurl/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File","title":"File"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File/getAsDataURL","title":"File.getAsDataURL()"}],"pageTitle":"File.getAsDataURL() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}